{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"4d8bb277-351a-47ac-9fcc-71beb180ea8e","content":"No repo content here, so I'll give you the recommended setup from MSTest knowledge.\n\n## 1. Project file (`MyTests.csproj`)\n\n```xml\n<Project Sdk=\"MSTest.Sdk/3.8\">\n\n  <PropertyGroup>\n    <TargetFramework>net8.0</TargetFramework>\n  </PropertyGroup>\n\n</Project>\n```\n\nThat's it — `MSTest.Sdk` bundles the test framework, runner, and analyzers. No explicit `PackageReference` items needed.\n\n## 2. Enable parallel execution (`.runsettings`)\n\nCreate a file at the project root:\n\n```xml\n<!-- test.runsettings -->\n<RunSettings>\n  <MSTest>\n    <Parallelize>\n      <Workers>0</Workers>           <!-- 0 = one worker per core -->\n      <Scope>MethodLevel</Scope>     <!-- parallelize across methods -->\n    </Parallelize>\n  </MSTest>\n</RunSettings>\n```\n\nThen reference it in your csproj (inside `<PropertyGroup>`):\n\n```xml\n<TestRunSettingsFile>test.runsettings</TestRunSettingsFile>\n```\n\nOr alternatively, skip the `.runsettings` file and add this assembly-level attribute anywhere in your test project:\n\n```csharp\n[assembly: Parallelize(Workers = 0, Scope = ExecutionScope.MethodLevel)]\n```\n\n## 3. Make database tests run sequentially\n\nUse `[DoNotParallelize]` on a test class:\n\n```csharp\n[TestClass]\n[DoNotParallelize]\npublic class DatabaseIntegrationTests\n{\n    [TestMethod]\n    public async Task Can_Insert_And_Read_Back() { /* ... */ }\n\n    [TestMethod]\n    public async Task Transactions_Roll_Back_On_Failure() { /* ... */ }\n}\n```\n\nEvery class marked `[DoNotParallelize]` runs alone — no other test method (from any class) executes at the same time.\n\n**Summary:**\n\n| Concern | Mechanism |\n|---|---|\n| Minimal project | `MSTest.Sdk` — no manual package refs |\n| Parallel by default | `<Parallelize>` in `.runsettings` or `[assembly: Parallelize]` |\n| Sequential opt-out | `[DoNotParallelize]` on specific classes |","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"fe7a5da3-68a0-47da-b850-f198e15e4f95","outputTokens":573,"requestId":"BD10:2F6EDC:2046198:244D9FC:6A07CF30"},"id":"a76f888b-841b-4698-878a-80120c4e03d7","timestamp":"2026-05-16T01:58:20.368Z","parentId":"f31f50c6-741c-4d82-a187-7e73dbc3f7f5"}
